{
  "texts": [
    "For each dataset, results are reported based on the best hyperparameter configuration for each chunker, determined by the average F1 score across all k values.",
    "All results to be reported below are obtained using dunzhang/stella_en_1.5B_v5 as the embedder for being the best among those tested.",
    "In the following subsections, Bold values indicate the best performance on the respective dataset.",
    "The results for Answer Generation closely matched those of Evidence Retrieval and are discussed in Appendix E.1.",
    "Additional analysis of hyperparameters is provided in Appendix B."
  ]
}